comments:
Abolished 1.4.1974 to become the Rother unparished area. See also Table 
    2, note (d).

Abolished 1.4.1956 and added to the parish of Camber. See 
    also Table 2, note (h).

Created 1.4.1956 from the parishes of Broomhill and Winchelsea 
    St. Thomas the Apostle. See also Table 2, note (k).

Abolished 9.11.1897 and divided between the parishes of Hollington 
    St. John and Hollington Rural.

Created 9.11.1897 out of the parishes of Hollington and St. Matthew. 
    Abolished 1.4.1925 and added to the parish of Hastings. See also Table 
    2, notes (e) and (f).

Created 9.11.1897 out of the rural parts of the parishes of Hollington 
    and St. Matthew. Abolished 1.4.1938 and divided between the parishes of Hastings, 
    Crowhurst and Westfield. See also Table 2, notes (e) and (j).
Created 1.4.1952 out of the parishes of Salehurst, Etchingham and Ticehurst. See also Table 2, note (k).

Abolished 1.4.1958 and divided between the parishes of Wivelsfield 
    and Guestling. See also Table 2, notes (g) and (j).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Bexhill. See also Table 2, note 
    (k).

That part which until 1894 formed part of the parish of 
    Bexhill. See also Table 2, note (d).

Abolished 1.4.1956 and added to the parish of Camber. See 
    also Table 2, note (h).
